[SN]TITLE[SN]
BBC Archive's guide to Burns Night

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
On the anniversary of his birth, people across Scotland and beyond are celebrating the poet Robert Burns.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
25 January 2016 Last updated at 17:33 GMT
But just what is the etiquette of Burns Night? Fret not, for BBC Rewind has scoured the archives and put together a comprehensive guide on how to celebrate Burns Night.
Have your haggis at the ready, some bagpipes at your side and prepare to raise a glass of whisky to Scotland's national bard.
